<h2 className="text-lg mt-0">Front — The Six</h2>
<ol className="list-decimal pl-4 text-sm space-y-1">
  <li>**Presence:** Show up—on time, eyes up.</li>
  <li>**Truth:** Confess fast; no spin.</li>
  <li>**Work:** Finish one thing daily.</li>
  <li>**Steward:** Budget, save, give.</li>
  <li>**Honor:** Dignify women &amp; elders.</li>
  <li>**Courage:** Do hard, right things.</li>
</ol>

<h2 className="text-lg mt-6">Back — The Six</h2>
<ol start={7} className="list-decimal pl-4 text-sm space-y-1">
  <li>**Speech:** No gossip or slander.</li>
  <li>**Learning:** Read, ask, practice.</li>
  <li>**Health:** Sleep, train, simple food.</li>
  <li>**Craft:** Build things that last.</li>
  <li>**Service:** Lift burdens at home first.</li>
  <li>**Faith:** Listen for God, obey promptly.</li>
</ol>

<div className="mt-4 flex justify-between items-end">
  <Caption>
    Review one standard daily. Recite the whole list weekly. A father-son pledge.
  </Caption>
